  "remarks": "JSC “Aviation Gearboxes and Transmissions – Perm Motors” manufactures and services helicopter gearboxes and transmissions for helicopters, including the Mi-28n “night hunter”, Mi-8/17 and Mi-26 (T). The Mi-28n “night hunter” has been used by the Russian military in its war of aggression against Ukraine. The company is a part of the holding company “Russian Helicopters”, which is subject to Union restrictive measures.",
